Interface TurnPhase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Attack, Fortification, ReEnforcement

    public interface TurnPhase
    TurnPHase interface declares method(s) for other concrete phases to implement This class is a part of State design pattern used for implementing player's phases.

    vanduong
